> **__Helpful Commands__**
.tag:intro
**__Introduction__**
This channel contains a list of all Clue Chasers discord commands along with a brief summary of what they contain. Feel free to use any of the commands in the <#333343575737892864> channel.

.
> __**Information Hub**__
.tag:infohub
⬥ `!gathering` - Links to the gathering section.
⬥ `!solving` - Links to the solving section.
⬥ `!faq` - Links to the faq section section.

.
> __**Globetrotter Outfit**__
.tag:goutfit
⬥ `!gjacket` - Explains the globetrotter jacket.
⬥ `!gbackpack` - Explains the globetrotter backpack.
⬥ `!garms` - Explains the globetrotter arm guards.
⬥ `!gshorts` - Explains the globetrotter shorts.
⬥ `!gboots` - Explains the globetrotter boots.

.
> __**Alchemical Items & Broadcasts**__
.tag:rewards
⬥ `!fortunates` - Lists every item that can be disassembled into a fortunate component.

.
> __**Abilities/Spells**__
.tag:spells
⬥ `!Surge` - Explains Surge.
⬥ `!Escape` - Explains Escape.
⬥ `!Dive` - Explains Dive.
⬥ `!Barge` - Explains Barge.
.

.
> __**Spreadsheets**__
.tag:sheets
⬥ `!hof` - Generates a link to Hall of Fame.
⬥ `!hardstepguide` - Generates a link to the hard clue step guide.

.
> __**Server Help**__
.tag:serverhelp
⬥ `!nav` - Lists some ways of navigating Clue Chasers.
⬥ `!notrading` - Shows our server rules and explains that trading is not allowed in our channels.
⬥ `!clue` - Generates an invite link for Clue Chasers.
⬥ `!cluehelp` - Links the Clue help forum and questions channel.
⬥ `!suggestion` - Links suggestions forum and offers examples of possible suggestions.
⬥ `!website` - Links the Clue Chasers website.
⬥ `!twitter` - Links the Clue Chasers twitter.

.
> __**Miscellaneous**__
.tag:misc
⬥ `!miscellaneous` - Placeholder.

.
